{"word":"G5052 - τελεσφορέω - telesphoréō - tel-es-for-eh'-o - Bring fruit to perfection","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τελεσφορέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">telesphoréō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tel-es-for-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bring fruit to perfection</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பலன்கொடு"},{"paragraph":"to bring to (perfection or) maturity"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G5056 - τέλος - télos - tel'-os/5056\">G5056</a> and <a href=\"#/G5342 - φέρω - phérō - fer'-o/5342\">G5342</a>; to <i>be a bearer to completion</i> (maturity), that is, to <i>ripen</i> fruit (figuratively): - bring fruit to perfection.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2005/2005\">G2005</a>, <a href=\"#/G3838/3838\">G3838</a>, <a href=\"#/G4930/4930\">G4930</a>, <a href=\"#/G4931/4931\">G4931</a>, <a href=\"#/G5046/5046\">G5046</a>, <a href=\"#/G5047/5047\">G5047</a>, <a href=\"#/G5048/5048\">G5048</a>, <a href=\"#/G5049/5049\">G5049</a>, <a href=\"#/G5050/5050\">G5050</a>, <a href=\"#/G5051/5051\">G5051</a>, <a href=\"#/G5052/5052\">G5052</a>, <a href=\"#/G5055/5055\">G5055</a>, <a href=\"#/G5056/5056\">G5056</a>"}]}